OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779451870
OL,3,CResidents fear dozens of HGVs will
OL,4,Ctravel in and out of their village
OL,5,Cdaily
OL,7,FThe residents of a small village have
OL,8,Ftold ITV Border about their concerns
OL,9,Fthat a large number of HGVs could
OL,10,Fstart travelling along its narrow and
OL,11,Fwindy roads.
OL,13,FBoreland, near Lockerbie, could see
OL,14,Fdozens of heavy goods vehicles travel
OL,15,Fin and out of the village daily, to
OL,16,Fmove excavation material from a new
OL,17,Fwater treatment site.
OL,19,FResidents say that they were told that
OL,20,Fthe material would be used to
OL,21,Flandscape the treatment site.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779451870
OL,3,CResidents fear dozens of HGVs will
OL,4,Ctravel in and out of their village
OL,5,Cdaily
OL,7,FAfter they approved the plans, they
OL,8,Fsay they found out this would not be
OL,9,Fthe case.
OL,11,FLocal resident Kate Nutt said: "We
OL,12,Fbelieve it's 110,000 cubic metres of
OL,13,Fsoil.
OL,15,F"The impact on the environment is
OL,16,Fgoing to be massive. We've asked why
OL,17,Fthere's been no environmental impact
OL,18,Fassessment done, and no-one will give
OL,19,Fus an answer.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779451870
OL,3,CResidents fear dozens of HGVs will
OL,4,Ctravel in and out of their village
OL,5,Cdaily
OL,7,F"Just in the local community, the
OL,8,Fpollution, the noise, impact on
OL,9,Fresidents' health and wellbeing is
OL,10,Fgoing to be huge."
OL,12,FRoss Dowie is a local farmer who uses
OL,13,Fquad bikes on the village roads.
OL,15,FHe told ITV Border: "I'm more
OL,16,Fconcerned about us being killed,
OL,17,Fbecause we drive quad bikes on this
OL,18,Froad.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779451870
OL,3,CResidents fear dozens of HGVs will
OL,4,Ctravel in and out of their village
OL,5,Cdaily
OL,7,F"There's a lot of sharp turns, long
OL,8,Fstretches, it's a massive worry. Every
OL,9,Ftime my wife goes out I don't know if
OL,10,Fshe's going to come back.
OL,12,F"I know it sounds a bit melodramatic,
OL,13,Fbut with the level of increase in
OL,14,Fvehicles, it's going to be off the
OL,15,Fcharts."
OL,17,FMembers of the local horse riding
OL,18,Fschool are also worried. The school
OL,19,Fuses local lanes daily to help people
OL,20,Fwith disabilities build confidence and
OL,21,Fmobility.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779451870
OL,3,CResidents fear dozens of HGVs will
OL,4,Ctravel in and out of their village
OL,5,Cdaily
OL,7,FOne of those riders, Charlotte
OL,8,FThompson, said: "It doesn't matter
OL,9,Fwhat we do, we still have to cross the
OL,10,Froad.
OL,12,F"I find it a bit upsetting...
OL,13,Fdepending on how quickly (the HGVs)
OL,14,Fcome and go."
OL,16,FLucie Dudgeon, meanwhile, is the
OL,17,Fparent of a service user.
OL,19,FShe said: "My daughter's got epilepsy
OL,20,Fand autism, so sounds and things going
OL,21,Fon around her do deeply impact her.
OL,26,@uD@ZpmuD@cpn
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779451870
OL,3,CResidents fear dozens of HGVs will
OL,4,Ctravel in and out of their village
OL,5,Cdaily
OL,7,F"I worry it will upset her and it will
OL,8,Fbe too much for her to cope with, and
OL,9,Fshe won't be able to come to her
OL,10,Fsessions any more.
OL,12,F"After coming for 15 years, and this
OL,13,Fbeing her only activity... for her to
OL,14,Flose that would be a massive
OL,15,Fdetriment."
OL,17,FThe transportation of excavated
OL,18,Fmaterial is set to last nine months.
OL,20,FResidents hope their concerns will be
OL,21,Fheard before it begins.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779451870
OL,3,CResidents fear dozens of HGVs will
OL,4,Ctravel in and out of their village
OL,5,Cdaily
OL,7,FIn response a Dumfries and Galloway
OL,8,FCouncil spokesperson said: "We're
OL,9,Faware of concerns raised by residents
OL,10,Fin Boreland about construction traffic
OL,11,Flinked to the proposed extension to
OL,12,FBlack Esk Water Treatment Works.
OL,14,F"The development was approved
OL,15,Ffollowing the statutory planning
OL,16,Fprocess, including public engagement
OL,17,Fand committee consideration. Through
OL,18,Fthe consultations carried out by both
OL,19,FScottish Water and Dumfries and
OL,20,FGalloway Council, only two objections
OL,21,Fwere received at the appropriate time.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779451870
OL,3,CResidents fear dozens of HGVs will
OL,4,Ctravel in and out of their village
OL,5,Cdaily
OL,7,F"Updated traffic information has
OL,8,Fraised new concerns, which officers
OL,9,Fare actively reviewing. No work can
OL,10,Fbegin until a detailed Construction
OL,11,FTraffic Management Plan is agreed,
OL,12,Fsetting out routes, safety measures
OL,13,Fand mitigation.
OL,15,F"This will not be approved until we
OL,16,Fare satisfied impacts are reduced to
OL,17,Fthe lowest practicable level.
OL,18,FAdditional safeguards, including
OL,19,Fmeasures to protect and repair roads,
OL,20,Fwill also be required.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779451870
OL,3,CResidents fear dozens of HGVs will
OL,4,Ctravel in and out of their village
OL,5,Cdaily
OL,7,F"Although some disruption during
OL,8,Fconstruction is unavoidable, it will
OL,9,Fbe temporary, and Scottish Water, as
OL,10,Fdeveloper, is responsible for
OL,11,Fminimising impacts and engaging with
OL,12,Fthe local community."
OL,14,FA Scottish Water spokesperson said:
OL,15,F"We recognise the concerns raised by
OL,16,Fresidents regarding construction
OL,17,Ftraffic associated with the Black Esk
OL,18,FWater Treatment Works project.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779451870
OL,3,CResidents fear dozens of HGVs will
OL,4,Ctravel in and out of their village
OL,5,Cdaily
OL,7,F"Following detailed geotechnical
OL,8,Finvestigations, it was determined that
OL,9,Fthe majority of excavated material is
OL,10,Funsuitable for reuse on site due to
OL,11,Fits composition and the environmental
OL,12,Frisks associated with storing it
OL,13,Fonsite.
OL,15,F"As a result, the removal of material
OL,16,Ffrom site is necessary to safely
OL,17,Fdeliver the project. The material will
OL,18,Fbe transported to a licensed local
OL,19,Fquarry facility in compliance with
OL,20,Fenvironmental and SEPA requirements.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779451870
OL,3,CResidents fear dozens of HGVs will
OL,4,Ctravel in and out of their village
OL,5,Cdaily
OL,7,F"Traffic volumes, routing and
OL,8,Fmitigation measures continue to be
OL,9,Fassessed through the Construction
OL,10,FTraffic Management Plan process in
OL,11,Fconsultation with Dumfries and
OL,12,FGalloway Council and relevant roads
OL,13,Fauthorities.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,360,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1779451870
OL,3,CResidents fear dozens of HGVs will
OL,4,Ctravel in and out of their village
OL,5,Cdaily
OL,7,F"The safety of the public, road users
OL,8,Fand the workforce remains Scottish
OL,9,FWater's highest priority, and all
OL,10,Fcontractors and drivers associated
OL,11,Fwith the project will be required to
OL,12,Fadhere to strict safety and
OL,13,Foperational standards throughout the
OL,14,Fconstruction period."
